  "definitions": {
    "b-label": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "FOOTPRINT BREAKDOWN",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug",
      "marginBottom": "0.5rem"
    },
    "b-energy": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Screen Energy\n\nThe average website produces **1.76g CO₂** per page view. A site with 100k monthly visits generates roughly the same emissions as **3 round-trip flights** from London to New York.\n\nDark themes, compressed assets, and no autoplay video are the fastest wins.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-paper": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Print Waste\n\nThe global printing industry produces **400 million tonnes** of paper annually. Designers routinely specify oversized print runs \"to be safe.\"\n\nDigital proofing, on-demand printing, and accurate forecasting reduce waste without compromise on quality.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.08
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-hardware": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Hardware Refresh\n\nDesign software demanding the latest hardware accelerates electronic waste. A 2022 survey found **67%** of designers replace their primary machine within 4 years.\n\nLighter software, better builds, and resisting the pull of unnecessary upgrades all extend device lifespans.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.16
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-longevity": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Design Longevity\n\nTrend-driven redesigns have real costs — both in production energy and in the discarded work they replace.\n\nDesigning for longevity is not nostalgia. It is an ecological position: work that lasts does not need to be remade. Systems over surfaces.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.24
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
